#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Mudutaravagga"
msgstr "2. Weaker"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Paṭhamasaṅkhittasutta"
msgstr "12. In Brief (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.12:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five faculties."

msgctxt "sn48.12:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn48.12:1.3"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ—"
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.12:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcindriyāni."
msgstr "These are the five faculties."

msgctxt "sn48.12:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ samattā paripūrattā arahaṃ hoti, "
"tato mudutarehi anāgāmī hoti, tato mudutarehi sakadāgāmī hoti, tato "
"mudutarehi sotāpanno hoti, tato mudutarehi dhammānusārī hoti, tato "
"mudutarehi saddhānusārī hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Someone who has completed and fulfilled these five faculties is a perfected "
"one. If they are weaker than that, they’re a non-returner. If they are "
"weaker still, they’re a once-returner. If they are weaker still, they’re a "
"stream-enterer. If they’re weaker still, they’re a follower of the "
"teachings. If they’re weaker still, they’re a follower by faith.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.12:1.6"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
